        Getting started
        ---------------
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            from mbq import metrics
        
            metrics.init(namespace='my-service', constant_tags={'env': ENV_NAME})
        
            metrics.increment('metric.name', 5, tags={'something': 'awesome'})
        
            # show the rest
        
